      "name": "Build-ApiDoc",
      "filePath": ".github/workflows/pages.yml",
      "summary": "在 GitLab Registry 的 Doxygen 容器中生成 API 参考文档，输出 CHM 和 HTML 两种格式。",
      "tags": ["build", "documentation", "doxygen", "api-reference"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "step:.github/workflows/pages.yml:Build-Pages",
      "type": "step",
      "name": "Build-Pages",
      "filePath": ".github/workflows/pages.yml",
      "summary": "使用 VitePress 构建文档静态站点，整合 API 文档，并通过 peaceiris/actions-gh-pages 部署到 opentap.github.io 外部仓库。",
      "tags": ["build", "documentation", "vitePress", "deployment"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "step:.github/workflows/pr-comment.yml:pr-version-comment",
      "type": "step",
      "name": "pr-version-comment",
      "filePath": ".github/workflows/pr-comment.yml",
      "summary": "在 main 分支推送后，调用 ghcr.io/asgeriversen/pr-version-comment 容器自动在关联 PR 和 Issue 上评论当前版本号信息。",
      "tags": ["automation", "pr-comment", "versioning"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    }
